replies.body:
I'm having trouble authenticating too, and I'm disconnecting from chat frequently. I get dropped before I can enter any lobbies. I feel like it started after I started getting an unusual 90ms ping in the Star Guardian gamemode. I think I was still receiving messages from the server, as I could see what my teammates were doing at normal ping. It didn't look like the server was getting my messages though, because I couldn't move my character or buy items. Every other service besides League is connecting with me just fine, and my cmd ping to the ip came back at my usual 60ms. I flushed my DNS, and my connection is normally good.

Real talk Broporo, is it because I haven't bought any Star Guardian skins yet? {{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} 

*Edit: Apparently it showed I was in a lobby with my friend, even though the client wasn't even running! I actually managed to get into a champ select phase... we'll see where it goes from here.
